short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Fast access to your Seedboxes.cc account

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: You can use this extension along with your Seedboxes.cc account, in order to quickly check your account's usage, receive product notifications or quickly perform actions on your account (restart, plex refresh) without the need to login to your client area.
